reviews.review_text: What a drag it is getting old. This fits right up there with just about every show they played after brent passed. Long story short jerry did appear on stage with what appeared to be his guitar and proceeded to look and play pretty freakened bored.I will keep it short jerry looked and played like he would've rather been ANYWHERE other than be on stage going thru the motions as he did thru most of the '90's.unless he was playing with his band or sittin' in with others.It wasn't like he set out to do it but 3rd or 4th song in it was obvious he was bored and really he was the one that could make or brake the tour,all in about an hours time.It was way more than obvious that he was not digging the grateful dead scene on any level and yeah it did hurt. After jumping around the world a few times it got old and no matter how deep he dug he couldn't talk himself into it.Well that is enough of that.I had always believed and still do IT IS ALL ABOUT THE MUSIC AND IT WILL ALWAYS BE THAT WAY.
